      "content": "i feel like i'm just being overly cautious. i've already looked up the tapering schedules and they say a week or two is plenty of time for the sertraline to clear out. if i wait a few days between the last pill and the first dose of st johns wort, isn't that basically solving the interaction problem? i just really need to know if it's actually okay to do this on my own so i can stop feeling like a zombie.",
